{"lemma":"عِوَضِ","slug":"عِوَضِ","root":"ع.#.ض","root_slug":"ع-_-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adv","noun","prep","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n31021","n31022"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to offset, to compensate, to substitute, to replace, to make up for"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَاضَ (ʕāḍa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"time – because as it passes it substitutes another portion of time","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"adv","gloss":"(with the present tense in the negative) ever, never, any time","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَاضَ (ʕāḍa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"substitute, something or someone instead of something or someone else"},{"pos":"prep","gloss":"in lieu of, instead of, in exchange of, in exchange for, in compensation for"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31021","headword_ar":"عَوْضُ","root":"EwD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDa","text_ar":"عَوْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, S, O, Mughnee, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDi","text_ar":"عَوْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mughnee, K,) the first accord. to Ks (TA) and the Koofees, and the second accord. to the Basrees; (O, TA; [in which latter it is added that the second is the most common; but this I think a mistake; for I have most frequently found the first; and in the Mughnee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDu","text_ar":"عَوْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is mentioned first, as in the S and K, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDa","text_ar":"عَوْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"last;]) indecl., (Mughnee, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabolu","text_ar":"قَبْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayona","text_ar":"اَيْنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amosi","text_ar":"اَمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mughnee,) without tenween; (S;) [but not always, as will be seen below;] an adv. n., (Mughnee, K,) denoting future time, (S, O,) or all future time, (Mughnee, K,) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~u","text_ar":"قَطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"denotes past time; (S, O;) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ever;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abadFA","text_ar":"اَبَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, * O, K;) but differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^badFA","text_ar":"ابَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"by being appropriated to negative phrases only: (Mughnee, K: *) you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^ufiAriquka EawoDu","text_ar":"لَا اُفِارِقُكَ عَوْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDu","text_ar":"عَوْضُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^ufaAriquka","text_ar":"لَا اُفَارِقُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not separate myself from thee, ever;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~u maA faAraqotuka","text_ar":"قَطُّ مَا فَارَقْتُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but you may not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDu maA faAraqotuka","text_ar":"عَوْضُ مَا فَارَقْتُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as you may not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~u maA A^ufaAriquka","text_ar":"قَطُّ مَا اُفَارِقُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) or it denotes past time also, having the same meaning: for you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotu mivolahu EawoDu","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُ مِثْلَهُ عَوْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, K,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not seen the like of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, ever:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ:) so in the two books [the O and the TS] of Sgh: and in like manner a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"falamo A^ara EaAmFA EawoDu A^akovara haAlikFA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And I have not seen a year, ever, more destructive"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) But it is decl. when prefixed to another noun; as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^foEaluhu EawoDa","text_ar":"لَا افْعَلُهُ عَوْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaAy^iDiyna","text_ar":"العَايِضِينَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mughnee, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not do it, ever;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A=tiyka EawoDa AlEaAy^iDiyna","text_ar":"لَا ا=تِيكَ عَوْضَ العَايِضِينَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not come to thee, ever"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahora Ald~aAhiriyna","text_ar":"دَهْرَ الدَّاهِرِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) [for in this case you may not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDu","text_ar":"عَوْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And one also says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfEl *aAka mino *iY EawoDK","text_ar":"افعل ذَاكَ مِنْ ذِى عَوْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in which the first word is written in some copies of the S and K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifoEalo","text_ar":"اِفْعَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in others"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoEalu","text_ar":"اَفْعَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino *iY A^unufK","text_ar":"مِنْ ذِى اُنُفٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino *iY","text_ar":"مِنْ ذِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabalK","text_ar":"قَبَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will do, that"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in what is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"now"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be begun"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immediately:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^unufN","text_ar":"اُنُفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O, K:) [thus making"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EwD","text_ar":"عوض"},{"kind":"text","text":"decl., and using it without a negative, which must always accompany it when it is indecl.] [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiwaDN","text_ar":"عِوَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDu","text_ar":"عَوْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~ahoru","text_ar":"الدَّهْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~amaAnu","text_ar":"الزَّمَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) which is thus called because, as often as a portion thereof passes, it substitutes for it another portion: (Mughnee, K:) or, as some say, because they assert that it despoils and gives compensation. (Mughnee.) [See an ex. in the Ham p. 271, where it occurs in this sense with tenween, in the printed text, though said in the commentary to be indecl., with fet-h or with damm.] Or it is an oath; (Ibn-El-Kelbee, Mughnee, K,) and is (so in the O and Mughnee, but in the K “ or ”) the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain idol, belonging to Bekr Ibn-Wáïl:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mughnee, O, K:) as in a verse cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mwr","text_ar":"مور"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, Mughnee:) but if so, there is no reason for its being used indeclinably in a verse of El-Aashà cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoHamu","text_ar":"اَسْحَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (Mughnee:) or it is a word used in the manner of an oath; a man saying to his companion,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoDu laA yakuwnu *`lika","text_ar":"عَوْضُ لَا يَكُونُ ذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abadFA","text_ar":"اَبَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nay, that will not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall not, be, ever"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: for if it were a noun signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it would be with tenween; but it is a particle by which is meant an oath, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajalo","text_ar":"اَجَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEamo","text_ar":"نَعَمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, O.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","O","K","AZ"]},{"entry_id":"n31022","headword_ar":"عِوَضٌ","root":"EwD","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A substitute; a thing given,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"received,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"done, instead"},{"kind":"text","text":"of,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in place"},{"kind":"text","text":"of,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in lieu"},{"kind":"text","text":"of, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in exchange"},{"kind":"text","text":"for, another thing;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a compensation; a thing given,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"received, by way of replacement;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badalN","text_ar":"بَدَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Msb;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEowaADN","text_ar":"اَعْوَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEuwDapN","text_ar":"مَعُوضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiwaDFA Eanohu","text_ar":"عِوَضًا عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As a substitute for it; instead of, in the place of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in exchange for, it; as a compensation for it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino *iY EiwaDK","text_ar":"مِنْ ذِى عِوَضٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn *Y EawoDK","text_ar":"من ذى عَوْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qbl","text_ar":"قبل"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["A","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}